    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>paste</strong> to a separate bowl with the <strong>grated</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Add 5 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[7 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[10 tbsp] </span><strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>tomato base</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
