            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray[s] from the oven and add your <strong>pizza base[s]</strong></p><p>Divide the <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>base</strong> between your <strong>pizza base[s] </strong>and spread it evenly all over them with the back of a spoon</p><p>Top with the <strong>meat-free mince </strong>and <strong>grated cheeze</strong></p><p>Tip: Make sure the pizza[s] don’t overlap on the tray[s] to avoid raw dough!</p>",
