    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>ketchup</strong> and <strong>mustard</strong> <strong>ketchup</strong> in a bowl with a splash of <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> – this is your <strong>burger sauce</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong> then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
