      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>plant-based cheezeburger pizza</strong> and top with the <strong>pickled</strong> <strong>shallot</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>burger sauce</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>salad</strong> and drizzle with a little <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
